rows.label: qst103610_msg0002
rows.name:
Me betray you?
You most biggest traitor of all!

rows.label: qst103610_msg0003
rows.name:
At least did good job weakening
anti-imperial forces inside Empire.
That Brionac lot was eyesore.

rows.label: qst103610_msg0004
rows.name:
But at far too high price. Thanks to you,
we lose valuable agents who infiltrate
our enemies, including Akatsuki!

rows.label: qst103610_msg0005
rows.name:
And you even bring unwanted guests
all the way here!
